title: Pacific Scoreboard: Oct. 26, 2015
text:
American School In Japan def. International School of the Sacred Heart 25-17, 25-15, 26-24 Monday at Tokyo Kills—ASIJ: Elyse Davidson 13, Savannah Napierski 8, Kiki Davidson 7; ISSH: Nina Warita 8, Kolora Momoedenu 7. Assists—ASIJ: Sammie Hoskins 28; ISSH: Mia Korver 10. Block points—ASIJ: Tanya Jackson 4; ISSH: Nina Warita 3. Noteworthy—Final home match for Mustangs coach Gail Lanier, who has been involved with the program on and off since 1977, 25 as head coach. 
South Korea 
Daegu High def. Humphreys High 25-25, 25-22, 25-23 Saturday at Camp Walker Aces—HHS: Dai’Jonnai Smith 9. Assists—HHS: Isabelle Ellsworth 15.
